  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Operations Manager (F&B)",
  "description": "<p>We are a growing Indian fusion bistro in Singapore seeking a <strong>hands-on Operations Manager</strong> to oversee daily restaurant operations, support both front and back of house teams, and ensure smooth, compliant, and efficient service.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Oversee daily bistro operations (FOH & BOH) to ensure service excellence</p></li><li><p>Manage staff rostering, attendance, manpower planning, and deployment</p></li><li><p>Supervise service standards, food quality, and customer experience</p></li><li><p>Work closely with the Head Chef to coordinate kitchen and service operations</p></li><li><p>Ensure compliance with <strong>NEA hygiene standards</strong>, workplace safety, and SOPs</p></li><li><p>Manage inventory, suppliers, ordering, and stock control</p></li><li><p>Handle customer feedback, service recovery, and operational issues</p></li><li><p>Monitor sales performance, costs, and operational efficiency</p></li><li><p>Prepare basic reports and support management in business planning</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum <strong>2 years’ experience</strong> in F&B operations or restaurant management</p></li><li><p>Strong leadership, communication, and people-management skills</p></li><li><p>Knowledge of <strong>Indian cuisine or Indian fusion concepts</strong> preferred</p></li><li><p>Familiar with Singapore F&B regulations and compliance standards</p></li><li><p>Hands-on, detail-oriented, and able to work in a fast-paced environment</p></li><li><p>Willing to work <strong>weekends, public holidays, and split shifts</strong></p></li></ul><p><strong>Additional Information</strong></p><ul><li><p>Location: Punggol, Singapore</p></li><li><p>Employment Type: Full-time</p></li><li><p><strong>Open to Singaporeans / PRs / eligible Work Pass holders</strong></p></li></ul><p>📩 <strong>To apply:</strong> Please send your CV and relevant experience to <strong>admin@ent-sg.com</strong></p>",
